# Reproducible plugin.zip — `pack` hashes the working tree, so line-ending drift
# (Windows core.autocrlf) makes the same commit produce a different sha256/size.
# Normalise text to LF; keep binaries untouched. (Save this file as `.gitattributes`.)
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
